# GitHub Copilot Configuration for MegiLance 2.0

**Purpose**: Optimize GitHub Copilot suggestion patterns for consistency with project standards.

---

## 🎯 Copilot Settings (VS Code)

Add to `.vscode/settings.json`:

```json
{
  "github.copilot.enable": {
    "plaintext": false,
    "markdown": false,
    "scm": false,
    "yaml": true,
    "python": true,
    "tsx": true,
    "typescript": true,
    "javascript": true,
    "css": false
  },
  "github.copilot.advanced": {
    "debug.overrideChatModel": "gpt-4o"
  },
  "editor.inlineSuggest.enabled": true,
  "editor.inlineSuggest.mode": "blockinline",
  "github.copilot.chat.launchChat": true,
  "github.copilot.chat.locales": ["en"],
  "diffEditor.ignoreTrimWhitespace": false,
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
  "python.defaultInterpreterPath": "${workspaceFolder}/backend/.venv/bin/python",
  "python.linting.pylintEnabled": true,
  "python.linting.pylintArgs": ["--disable=C0111,C0103"],
  "[python]": {
    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "ms-python.python"
  },
  "[typescript]": {
    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
    "editor.codeActionsOnSave": {
      "source.fixAll.eslint": "explicit"
    }
  },
  "[tsx]": {
    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
  }
}
```

