## 🤖 Copilot Chat Prompts (Quick Commands)

Save these as snippets or Copilot commands:

### Backend (Python/FastAPI)
```
@copilot /fix-types - Add type hints to function
@copilot /add-docstring - Generate comprehensive docstring
