## 🤖 Copilot Slash Commands Reference

| Command | Use Case | Example |
|---------|----------|---------|
| `/explain` | Understand complex code | `/explain how this async function works` |
| `/tests` | Generate test cases | `/tests for the validateEmail function` |
| `/fix` | Suggest bug fixes | `/fix the memory leak in this component` |
| `/doc` | Generate documentation | `/doc this API endpoint` |
| `/refactor` | Suggest improvements | `/refactor this component for performance` |
| `/review` | Code review suggestions | `/review this authentication flow` |

