## 🎯 Preferred Copilot Behaviors

### ✅ ALWAYS Suggest
- [ ] Type hints for function parameters
- [ ] Comprehensive docstrings
- [ ] Error handling with try-catch
- [ ] Unit test files
- [ ] Pydantic schemas for validation
- [ ] ARIA attributes for accessibility
- [ ] CSS modules over inline styles
- [ ] Async/await for I/O operations

### ❌ NEVER Suggest (Disable)
- [ ] Inline comments for obvious code
- [ ] Deprecated packages
- [ ] Breaking style changes
- [ ] SQL queries (use ORM)
- [ ] Hardcoded secrets/tokens
- [ ] Global state mutations
- [ ] Synchronous API calls

### ⚠️ Suggest with Caution
- [ ] Complex regex patterns (verify correctness)
- [ ] Database migrations (review carefully)
- [ ] Authentication logic (security audit needed)
- [ ] Third-party library versions (check compatibility)
- [ ] Performance optimizations (measure before/after)

