## 🎓 Training Copilot for Your Project

### Week 1: Learn Patterns
1. Share frontend component structure (Button, Card, Form)
2. Share backend router structure (auth, projects)
3. Show type definitions and schemas
4. Provide CSS module examples

### Week 2: Specialized Knowledge
1. Show testing patterns (Jest, Pytest)
2. Share database query patterns (ORM usage)
3. Provide accessibility requirements
4. Show error handling patterns

### Week 3: Refinement
1. Review Copilot suggestions
2. Provide feedback on patterns Copilot misses
3. Share specific project conventions
4. Refinement based on actual usage

