## 📞 Troubleshooting Copilot

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| No suggestions appearing | Check extension enabled, GitHub logged in, file saved |
| Suggestions are irrelevant | Provide more context in chat, share related code |
| Copilot suggests deprecated code | Update training with current patterns |
| Performance suggestions wrong | Review and modify; Copilot may not know project constraints |
| Type hints missing in suggestions | Add types to function signature first |

