## ✅ Copilot Acceptance Criteria

Verify Copilot suggestions meet these before accepting:

- [ ] **Types**: All parameters and returns typed (TypeScript)
- [ ] **Tests**: Proposed code includes test cases
- [ ] **Accessibility**: ARIA labels present where needed
- [ ] **Security**: No hardcoded secrets, proper validation
- [ ] **Style**: Matches project code style and patterns
- [ ] **Performance**: No N+1 queries, efficient algorithms
- [ ] **Error Handling**: Graceful error messages
- [ ] **Documentation**: Functions have docstrings
- [ ] **Dependencies**: Uses existing libraries (no new packages)
- [ ] **Backwards Compatible**: No breaking changes

